
> Section 3 - @possess
>
> @possess [off|<player_name>]
>
> This command either turns possession off, if the keyword 'off' is used
> as an argument, possesses a player, or reports which player is being
> possessed, if no argument is passed.
>
> All text sent to a possessed player (apart from possession reports) is
> sent to the possessing player; furthermore, all commands prepended with
> a '$' character will be enacted by the possessed player.
>
> See Also: @force(3)

